    <meta property="og:description" content="Dear user, thank you for being a part of Word Power Swahili Dictionary, for it to improve and grow bigger we are requesting everyone to be a contributor of words, phrases and their meaning. We will appreciate for your support on success and growth of our largest online dictionary" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="" />
